title Web Component Consuming Asynchronous API

participant User
participant WebComponent
participant AsyncAPI

User->WebComponent: Interact (e.g., click)
activate WebComponent
WebComponent->WebComponent: Show loading indicator
WebComponent->AsyncAPI: Send async request
activate AsyncAPI
note over AsyncAPI: Process request
AsyncAPI-->WebComponent: Return async response
deactivate AsyncAPI
WebComponent->WebComponent: Hide loading indicator
WebComponent->WebComponent: Update UI with response
deactivate WebComponent
